data.description: Welcome to this Immaculate 5 Bed 4 Full Bath and 2 half baths well maintain home. Nestled in King's Grant at Liberty Hill. Become greeted by a magnificent staircase and 2 story foyers. In the executive style kitchen, you will notice gleaming granite countertops state-of-the art stainless steel appliances. That include double wall ovens & a 5 Bunner gas top stove. Massive granite kitchen island for prep space & storage on both sides. In-law suite downstairs with full bath attached. Great room as well formal dining room, formal living room. 2 Car garage attached side entry with additional storage space & mud room. Upstairs you have two bedrooms attached to a Jack&Jill bath. As well an oversized bedroom with attached full bath. Massive Luxury master suite with its very own attached sitting room with gas fireplace. Third floor bonus room with half bath. This smart style over 4,300 sqft property comes with solar panels, tankless hot water heater as well water softer system. Welcome home.
